channel.title: Want a server of your own?
channel.description:

[size=24pt][center]Well now you can![/center] [size=18pt][center]All u gotta do is add my msn[/center] [center]Zam500500@hotmail.com[/center]
[center]We will make a 508 or 525[/center] [center]Plus you also need requirements[/center]

[center]So if u want your own add my msn![/center] [center]No need to pay me or anything[/center] [center]I will tell you what to do and how to code![/center]
[color=blue][center][size=36pt]Thanks[/size][/center] [center][size=32pt]~~~Dan~~~[/size][/center]
